query: INSERT INTO course_enrollments (userId, bundleId, enrollmentType, paymentStatus, amountPaid, status, progress) SELECT userId, 1, 'bundle', 'completed', 99900, 'enrolled', 0 FROM (SELECT userId FROM course_enrollments WHERE courseId IS NOT NULL GROUP BY userId HAVING COUNT(*) = 7 LIMIT 1) AS subquery;
